Class OrdersService

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.application.startUp.demo.services.OrdersService

  • @Service
public class OrdersService
extends Object
    A class that contains all the logic to save sandwiches ordered with or whitout extra ingredients, save extra ingredient of each sandwiches and save the order.

        Returns:
        return true if the quantity of extra meat present in the sandwich is more than one.

      • verifiIfHasPromotionLight

        protected Boolean verifiIfHasPromotionLight()
        Method which verify and return if a sandwich belongs to light promotion or not. The method verify two variables to see if bacon and lettuce are present in a sandwich, if bacon is present the promotion is not applicable, otherwise if bacon is not present but lettuce is present the promotion is applicable.
        Returns:
        a boolean true if bacon is not present but luttuce is.
